query:
SELECT st.id, st.customerId, st.amount, st.status, st.sessionId, c.email, c.name 
FROM stripe_transactions st 
LEFT JOIN customers c ON st.customerId = c.id 
WHERE st.amount = 2000 
ORDER BY st.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 1
